{"tid":943369,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"「幣少」推介加密貨幣FCC 被捕後一度急跌7成","createTime":"2018-12-16T13:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T13:56:48.000Z","uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f3211932673758ec9e1c6c189ae9ef46113a719a","tid":943369,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181216/large/1544958402_ed83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181216%2Flarge%2F1544958402_ed83.jpg&h=53fa55b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自稱「香港區塊鏈第一人」的「幣少爺」黃鉦傑，在網上聲稱靠加密貨幣Bitcoin致富，並指所提供的礦機可以掘出一款基於IPFS技術衍生、名為「Filecash coin」（FCC）的加密貨幣，邀請市民參加掘礦，FCC並在日前正式於內地交易平台上市，惟Filecash coin在幣少被捕後雪崩式暴跌，單日跌幅一度達7成。<br />\n<br />\n根據加密貨幣交易平台幣虎顯示，自「幣少爺」黃鉦傑下午1時於深水埗現身後，其價格一直下降，由原本的約14美元左右，跌至約10美元，至「幣少」於下午3時55分被帶上警車後，其價格突然急劇下跌，一度低見4.73元，較高位急跌7成。<br />\nFilecash coin於12月初正式於內地交易平台幣虎「上市」，短短數日由0.3美元升至逾14美元高位。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181216/59037060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59037060&d=o63dqAD8vxmsRe%2FP1KBI0%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=c0937eaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181216%2F59037060&h=c388b323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181216/59037060</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f28e84bb47a7614fcdded30c80a41efc9f1ea8","tid":943369,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T13:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as